dct_title_s: Yosemite : Wawona route via Mariposa Big Trees, Inspiration Point and Glacier Point [side 2]
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures and spot heights. Panel title. Insets: photographs of Yosemite. "Drawn by J.C. Henkenius." Originally issued folded to 20 x 10 cm. Yosemite Valley and Mariposa Big Tree Grove, re-ceded to the U.S. by California in 1905, are shown with separate boundaries. Railroad line, opened in 1907, is not shown--Cf. Russell, C.P. One hundred years in Yosemite. 1947. p. 187.
dct_publisher_sm: San Francisco : Yosemite Stage & Turnpike Co., [ca. 1904]
